description:
At the DMV, underpaid employees deal with irritated customers all day long, yet Colette (Harriet Dyer) remains upbeat. Her driving test takes an unsettling turn with an intense creepy applicant, while Vic (Tony Cavalero) sneaks a drive-thru order during his own test. Meanwhile, Greg (Tim Meadows) faces a hoarder’s car packed with trash, ending in total chaos. Season 1, Episode 1: Pilot.
